### Profile Identity API (requires auth cookie or Bearer token)

### Get profile (extended identity payload)
GET http://localhost:5000/profile

### Titles
GET http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/titles

PUT http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/titles/equip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titleId": "explorer"
}

PUT http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/titles/unequip

### Badges
GET http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/badges

GET http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/badges/unlocked

PUT http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/badges/equip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "badgeId": "member_badge"
}

PUT http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/badges/unequip

### Achievements
GET http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/achievements

### Avatars (unlock-aware catalog)
GET http://localhost:5000/profile/identity/avatars
